		<P>This list is for questions, issues, comments, and general discussion of ZFS and ZFS related issues.</P>
	  <p> To see the collection of prior postings to the list,
	      visit the <a href="http://lists.macosforge.org/pipermail/zfs-discuss/">zfs-discuss
		  Archives</a>.
	      
	  </p>
	</TD>
      </TR>
